{
  "stem": "26022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, that particular house that we were sent to was on a very prestigious street and a very big, beautiful house, with a large courtyard and a wing in the back.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the front was all occupied by Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they brought as many Jews-- there were Jews living there already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a fairly Jewish section.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they brought as many Jews as they could into the existing apartments of the Jews who lived there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was-- we were sent to a very nice old lady and her spinster daughter, who had a-- an apartment of three rooms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So they got to keep one room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another room, a Jewish journalist was sent to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there was a room right off the corridor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now this is four flights up, a big stone staircase-- cold-- and mother and I got that room, which used to be their dining room because there was still a great, big [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] breakfront in there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got two [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] makeshift beds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately, there were a lot of bedbugs, not only in those beds, but in the building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't know whether that was worse, or the fact that it was under the roof and the roof leaked, so that we had to go to bed on rainy days with the umbrella open.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, no, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was strictly a Nazi thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, the Jewish community had another terrible task.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll tell you about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, we got this card that we have to leave the apartment in 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to go to city hall.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
